Pocket Block - Merge Numbers is a number merge puzzle  brain game with great fun.

◈ Simple & Pixel art graphics designed. Beautiful UI and magic colorful tiles.
◈ Smooth gaming experience.
◈ Games without wifi, don't require wifi, offline play! You can play it any time, any where.
◈ Also fun for teens, play with your kids.
◈ Leaderboard supported! Compete with players all over the world!
◈ This game support manual save. You can save the progress and continue next time.
◈ 100% native support. 
◈ Free to play.
◈ Simple game rules. You can learn it by practice.
◈ Full of skills. You can develop the skill to reach higher score.
◈ No time limit to play. Just play happy and relaxing.
◈ Easy to control, just swipe swipe swipe, tap tap tap.

Download and joint the Pocket Block - Merge Numbers world! Just have fun and try this addicting and challenging game.

